Welcome to Ultimate Surrender's Tag Team League.
Team Orange vs Team Red. Four girls,
non-scripted, real tag team action.
The rules are set: (1) Three tags per team, per round.
(2) Three 12-minute non-scripted wrestling rounds. (3)
Last round consists of the winners tying up,
dominating, humiliating, and brutally fucking the
losers. IN FRONT OF A LIVE AUDIENCE!
Team Orange: Without a single win under their belts this season, Orange is already out of the playoff picture. With one shot left to prove that they are not the worst team of the league, Orange is put to the test with a true challenge in round 3.
Team Red: The stakes for Red are high this match. Winning means they will be strong contenders for the final championship. Losing means that they were beat by the worst team in the league. Ariel X with new team member Jennifer Dark, as Samantha Sin's replacement, show team orange that they are hungry for victory!
